By carefully designing your Flink job to include detailed audit logging and appropriate windowing strategies, you can ensure that your system complies with MiFID II requirements. This approach not only helps in analyzing order lifecycle metrics but also provides the necessary traceability and transparency required by regulatory standards.

This setup ensures robustness, compliance, and high-quality data processing for financial services applications.

